subject: Optimization of VPD collection process.
commitMessage:
Optimization of VPD collection process.

This commit implement changes to optimize the process of VPD
collection.
It is achieved by storing the FRU specific SN and FN keyword offset
in persistent memory and using the same to fetch the value of
these keywords in case of system reboot or service reset.
If the value of these keywords, already on DBus, matches to the value
read from the VPD file of the given FRU using the offset stored,
it can be assumed that there is no change in the FRU and re-collection
of VPD for the given FRU is not required.

Meson Compilation: OK

Test Case execution: OK
